       * Higher values produce finer pixel grids. Range: 1–64.
       */
      pixelDensity: z.number().min(1).max(64).optional(),

      /**
       * Output image format.
       * Defaults to `"png"` when not specified.
       */
      outputFormat: z.enum(['png', 'jpeg']).optional(),
    }),
  ),
);

